{"tid":696225,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【你肯賠 政府有話過收？】C朗賠款1.75億了結逃稅案","createTime":"2018-06-10T01:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T02:21:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d36ac2ed51fab21b6dda4ce8f4911aaf3a13d3","tid":696225,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"涉嫌逃稅的皇家馬德里球星C朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo），近日和西班牙稅務部門達成協議，決定賠款1900萬歐元（約1.75億港元，下同），平息稅務風波。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據西班牙傳媒指，C朗承認逃稅等四項指控，表示願意賠款1900萬歐元平息事件。西班牙稅務部門指收到賠款後會撤銷起訴，了結官司。<br />\n<br />\n去年中，西班牙馬德里檢察院指控C朗，在2011至2014年間逃稅1475萬歐元（約1.36億港元），當時C朗出庭否認控罪。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙傳媒曾指球星逃稅的情況非常普遍，現時西班牙政府對球員徵收50%薪俸稅，故中國社會科學院歐洲研究所研究員趙俊傑認爲，球星逃稅與當地高稅率及稅率調節有關。"},{"pid":"035ad0a6a84792791670e99633bb2232924bdde7","tid":696225,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"達成協議"},{"pid":"58a0df32eabfba3f47a6733c2c03eb6a42c04049","tid":696225,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaff33d020e1abbc0e807c4082e3483984271b9","tid":696225,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"王騎冇得再j c朗逃稅了"},{"pid":"b61107f49617c6b4f60886d5854a7d73d5a9813c","tid":696225,"uid":17474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"咁依家政府收唔收呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6cc8ebe80a4ab7161a221de7fac14e01162810","tid":696225,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c51d2daa98a6e02ba25f9658646170a777fe9fb2","tid":696225,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"又話牙朗冇罪，係咩合法避稅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要認罪牙？"},{"pid":"d1faa17a8a5c7eedcc26d